INPUT
-> Texture coordinate         start node, select 'object' if you want add texture to you object


TEXTURE
-> Image texture              if you want upload image as texture 
-> Noise texture              if you want upload noise as texture (use fac for procedural)


COLOR
-> RGB Curves                 if you want to get more or less saturation of color
-> Mix RGB                    merge two RGB channel


VECTOR
-> Bump                       depth through normal changeÑ‹


CONVERTER
-> Color Ramp                 overall gradient control (like example use 'Noise texture' + 'Color Ramp')


______________
N O T E S

Ctrl + T                       add 'Texture coordinate' and 'Mapping' nodes








